                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.51/4411: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schurman</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-10-08T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 8, 1923—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>214. Your 326, September 29, 4 p.m.</p>
                <p>Department perceives no objection to acceptance by American Group representative
                    of advisership to Financial Readjustment Commission, and Group has been so
                    advised.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
